{
  "stem": "25027.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had one faucet like in the middle of a town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody used to come with pails.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to carry the water home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had outhouses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a little shack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to go outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And twice a year, a man used to come and empty it out with a barrel and a horse, real modern.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I went to school, the area where I went to school was mostly a Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived like in a isolated ghetto part, mostly poor Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the school was run by the Polish government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say that about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 30% or 40% of the students were Polish and Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, most Polish students and Ukrainian students were going to their own parochial, church-sponsored schools in those days.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a predominantly Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the curriculum was in Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And most of the teachers, I would say, were anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had-- classes began in the morning with a religious-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] everybody had to stand up and pray-- though I kept my mouth shut, I didn't say anything-- in a Catholic-Christian prayer, which I still remember.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they were very rough, the way they treated to us as Jews with remarks, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in general, you could feel the anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could feel it as a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was hit a few times with a long ruler, yelled at, screamed at.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the teachers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a few encounters there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you would expect children to fight in classes, but to be called continuously dirty Jew, [NON-ENGLISH] which means filthy, full of vermin Jew, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
